{"id": "4905", "revid": "43707339", "url": "https://helldivers.fandom.com/wiki?curid=4905", "title": "Activate E-710 Pumps", "text": "Gameplay.\n&lt;br&gt;\nThe Activate E-710 Pumps, as the briefing states, consists of finding the local E-710 Extractors and reactivating them. Being rather simple and only found as a primary objective on Easy and Medium difficulties (seen as sub objectives on higher difficulties), the Helldiver must simply go to the location, activate the terminal and follow the directional input prompt to begin working on the objective. After which the mission becomes quite similar to the &lt;a href=\"Pump%20Fuel%20to%20ICBM\"&gt;Pump Fuel to ICBM&lt;/a&gt; mission, where the Helldiver must reallocate the fuel from the local storage to the Transfer Station, then turn multiple valves to open the flow, then finally finishing with a single tap on the terminal."}
