{"id": "3880", "revid": "55339407", "url": "https://helldivers.fandom.com/wiki?curid=3880", "title": "Cannon Tower", "text": "Cannon Tower.\nThe Cannon Tower is a static weapon emplacement widely used by the &lt;a href=\"Automatons\"&gt;Automatons&lt;/a&gt; to defend their territory. The cannon is virtually identical to the cannon of an &lt;a href=\"Tank\"&gt;Annihilator Tank&lt;/a&gt;, except placed on a tall pyramid-like base. They are typically seen guarding large automaton bases with a smaller chance to be at medium outposts. A direct hit from the Cannon can kill a Helldiver and near misses will send them flying. They also have incredibly high range, making them a constant danger in relatively open areas. \nThey are typically considered high priority when dealing with the base they're guarding due to their high lethality and range. However, they turn slowly, making it harder to track Helldivers that are closer to the Cannon. They also typically only respond to action in front of them, or by being alerted by other attacks on Automaton structures and units. Stealth or running near the base of the cannon can be an effective way to reach the heatsink weakspot on the side opposite to the barrel, though it is usually guarded. "}
