{"id": "6763", "revid": "46883485", "url": "https://helldivers.fandom.com/wiki?curid=6763", "title": "Elevated Overseer", "text": "The Elevated Overseer is a flying &lt;a href=\"Illuminate\"&gt;Illuminate&lt;/a&gt; medium infantry unit, equipped with a gun that shoots plasma pellets, high explosive grenades, and a hoverpack. These troops share a similar role to the &lt;a href=\"Overseer\"&gt;Overseer&lt;/a&gt;, appearing in-between hordes of the &lt;a href=\"Voteless\"&gt;Voteless&lt;/a&gt;.\nAppearance.\nElevated Overseers sport similar aesthetics and armor to their &lt;a href=\"Overseer\"&gt;ground-bound compatriots&lt;/a&gt;, which is grey with purple accents. What sets them apart however, are the large twin-turbine jetpacks mounted behind them, which elevates them off the ground.\nThey appear in Difficulty 3 and above, typically guarding outposts or joining patrols around the map."}
{"id": "5164", "revid": "34624864", "url": "https://helldivers.fandom.com/wiki?curid=5164", "title": "Eliminate (Objective)", "text": "Eliminate is a mission that can be compared to a hunt/assassination of sorts, where the Helldivers insert into an area and kill the specific targeted enemy. There are different versions of this mission depending on the difficulty and enemy faction the Helldiver is attacking, ranging from smaller enemies such as a Brood Commander and Devastator, all the way up to Bile Titans and Factory Striders.\nThe mission will always have a large ring on the map indicating the general location of the target(s) and the Helldivers must find the targets within the radius of it. The search area often overlaps with outposts, in some cases close enough to attract the attention of massive high-value targets.\nSee the enemy's respective pages to find the best way to eliminate them.\n= =\n&lt;a href=\"Brood%20Commander\"&gt;Brood Commander&lt;/a&gt;.\nDifficulties:\nNumber of Targets:\n&lt;a href=\"Charger\"&gt;Charger&lt;/a&gt;.\nDifficulties: \nNumber of Targets:\n&lt;a href=\"Bile%20Titan\"&gt;Bile Titan&lt;/a&gt;.\nDifficulties:\nNumber of Targets:\n&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;\n&lt;br&gt;\n= =\n&lt;a href=\"Devastator\"&gt;Devastator&lt;/a&gt;.\nDifficulties: \nNumber of Targets: \n&lt;a href=\"Hulk\"&gt;Hulk&lt;/a&gt;.\nDifficulties: \nNumber of Targets: \n&lt;a href=\"Factory%20Strider\"&gt;Factory Strider&lt;/a&gt;.\nDifficulties: \nNumber of Targets: \n= =\n&lt;a href=\"Harvester\"&gt;Harvester&lt;/a&gt;.\nDifficulties: \nNumber of Targets: "}
