{"id": "6015", "revid": "37419324", "url": "https://helldivers.fandom.com/wiki?curid=6015", "title": "Hydrobius", "text": "Hydrobius is one of the five planets that reside within the &lt;a href=\"Omega%20Sector\"&gt;Omega Sector&lt;/a&gt;.\nTopography.\nSimilar to &lt;a href=\"Ustotu\"&gt;Ustotu&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href=\"Erata%20Prime\"&gt;Erata Prime&lt;/a&gt; and &lt;a href=\"Erson%20Sands\"&gt;Erson Sands&lt;/a&gt;.\nHistory.\nSecond Galactic War.\nReturn of the Illuminate.\nHydrobius was a peaceful colony in the southern galactic rim, having been colonized after the &lt;a href=\"First%20Galactic%20War\"&gt;First Galactic War&lt;/a&gt; but without much other events to really highlight since. However, things weren't fated to remain in this state of calm stillness for much longer.\nOn December 21st, 2184, the launched an assault onto Hydrobius, hours before their prior raids at &lt;a href=\"Osupsam\"&gt;Osupsam&lt;/a&gt; and &lt;a href=\"Baldrick%20Prime\"&gt;Baldrick Prime&lt;/a&gt; came to an end. Even though the Helldivers had orders to secure the &lt;a href=\"Umlaut%20Sector\"&gt;Umlaut Sector&lt;/a&gt;, a contingent would divert to help repel the Illuminate raid, hoping to prevent the plunder of its resources and guarantee the safety of its citizens."}
