{"id": "3710", "revid": "55339407", "url": "https://helldivers.fandom.com/wiki?curid=3710", "title": "JAR-5 Dominator", "text": " \nThe JAR-5 Dominator is a unique weapon firing two-stage, jet-propelled ammunition that explodes upon entering a target. Capable of medium armor penetration, the Dominator excels at defeating larger, moderately-armored foes such as &lt;a href=\"Hive%20Guard\"&gt;Hive Guards&lt;/a&gt; and &lt;a href=\"Devastator\"&gt;Devastator&lt;/a&gt;s, but struggles against groups of enemy fodder due to high recoil, low rate of fire, and limited ammo capacity.\nThe Dominator can be unlocked via the third page of &lt;a href=\"Steeled%20Veterans\"&gt;Warbond: Steeled Veterans&lt;/a&gt;.\n&lt;a href=\"Know%20Your%20Role\"&gt;Role&lt;/a&gt;:.\nThe Dominator is optimal for dealing with moderately-armored targets or enemies with larger health pools like &lt;a href=\"Hive%20Guard\"&gt;Hive Guards&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href=\"Brood%20Commander\"&gt;Brood Commanders&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href=\"Devastator\"&gt;Devastator&lt;/a&gt;s, or &lt;a href=\"Scout%20Strider\"&gt;Scout Strider&lt;/a&gt;s, and is best paired with a support weapon stratagem that is ideal for clearing crowds of fodder enemies such as the &lt;a href=\"M-105%20Stalwart\"&gt;Stalwart&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href=\"MG-43%20Machine%20Gun\"&gt;Machine Gun&lt;/a&gt;, or especially the &lt;a href=\"ARC-3%20Arc%20Thrower\"&gt;Arc Thrower&lt;/a&gt;, Grenade Launcher, or &lt;a href=\"FLAM-40%20Flamethrower\"&gt;Flamethrower&lt;/a&gt;."}
{"id": "3293", "revid": "55339407", "url": "https://helldivers.fandom.com/wiki?curid=3293", "title": "Jin Xi Sector", "text": "The Jin Xi Sector is a inhabited area of galaxy on the &lt;a href=\"Eastern%20Front\"&gt;Eastern Front&lt;/a&gt; in &lt;a href=\"Helldivers%202\"&gt;Helldivers 2&lt;/a&gt;. Located on galactic far east from &lt;a href=\"Super%20Earth\"&gt;Super Earth&lt;/a&gt;, it consists of 6 colonized systems and is named after &lt;a href=\"https%3A//en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Jin_Xi_%28Han%29\"&gt;Jin Xi&lt;/a&gt;, an ancient Chinese general under Emperor Liu Bang.\nThe Jin Xi Sector had yet to be colonized by the start of the second galactic war, with those Colonies that had been settled since being only weeks old before a massive &lt;a href=\"Terminids\"&gt;terminid&lt;/a&gt; outbreak erupted out of &lt;a href=\"The%20Gloom\"&gt;The Gloom&lt;/a&gt; into the Jin Xi Sector. Millions of families were trapped within, awaiting emergency evacuation as all Helldivers were called to the colonies' defense during Operation Overrun."}
