{"id": "3758", "revid": "1524681", "url": "https://helldivers.fandom.com/wiki?curid=3758", "title": "Martyrs' Day", "text": "Super Earth has many holidays. And Martyrs' Day is one of them.\nIt is customary for the Citizens to celebrate the Day by buying gifts such as Helldivers toys, Helldiver's mockup helmets, toy statues of fallen heroes of the past or even real equipment from recently deceased troops. Buying such things is equivalent to buying war bonds, because significan part of the revenue goes to the armed forces of Super Earth."}
