{"id": "5991", "revid": "37419324", "url": "https://helldivers.fandom.com/wiki?curid=5991", "title": "Osupsam", "text": "Osupsam is one of the five planets that reside within the &lt;a href=\"Tarragon%20Sector\"&gt;Tarragon Sector&lt;/a&gt;.\nTopography.\nSimilar to &lt;a href=\"Zagon%20Prime\"&gt;Zagon Prime&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href=\"Phact%20Bay\"&gt;Phact Bay&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href=\"Durgen\"&gt;Durgen&lt;/a&gt; and &lt;a href=\"Choohe\"&gt;Choohe&lt;/a&gt;.\nHistory.\nSecond Galactic War.\nReturn of the Illuminate.\nOsupsam was a peaceful planet colony of Super Earth in the Southern Galactic Rim. Having been settled after the &lt;a href=\"First%20Galactic%20War\"&gt;First Galactic War&lt;/a&gt;, its history was very uneventful. Presumably, it found enough economic success to finance the construction of more urbanized settlements at some point prior to its involvement in the ongoing Second Galactic War.\nHowever, Osupsam was not going to be allowed to live in peace for much longer. On December 22nd, 2184. The attacked in tandem with &lt;a href=\"Baldrick%20Prime\"&gt;Baldrick Prime&lt;/a&gt;, following a series of raid that had been going on since the week prior.\nThe Helldivers, being occupied with the ongoing Operation Wormhole Spaghetti at the &lt;a href=\"Umlaut%20Sector\"&gt;Umlaut Sector&lt;/a&gt;, would only be able to dispatch a fraction of its forces to help contain the Illuminate raiders.\nAfter 12 hours of battle, the Helldivers wouldn't be able to defeat the Illuminate raiders, who plundered all of what they could and then left."}
{"id": "5952", "revid": "54761251", "url": "https://helldivers.fandom.com/wiki?curid=5952", "title": "Outpost 32", "text": "Outpost 32 is one of four planets that reside in the &lt;a href=\"Saleria%20Sector\"&gt;Saleria Sector&lt;/a&gt;.\nHistory.\nFirst Galactic War.\nDuring the First Galactic War Outpost 32 was on the Cyborg front. Outpost 32 saw lots of fighting during the war, it was nearly impossible for a Helldiver to complete a mission on the planet. It is considered to be the &lt;a href=\"Malevelon%20Creek\"&gt;Malevelon Creek&lt;/a&gt; of the &lt;a href=\"First%20Galactic%20War\"&gt;First Galactic War&lt;/a&gt;.\nSecond Galactic War.\nOutpost 32 has had no significance during the war, posters reading \"Remember Outpost 32\" can be found at POI's, serving as a grim reminder of the horrors that took place there. With recent events on Calypso, citizens on Outpost 32 have been placed on standby for evacuations."}
